ike":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T12:05:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>次次book完都會send email問<br />\n就算唔係所會print定張單到時可以show比reception睇</blockquote><br />\n比張單佢睇 佢都可以唔認你張單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你訓到凌晨佢都開你門話間房唔係你嘅添呀</blockquote><br />\n仲有次試過CHECK OUT左先話間房唔係我呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83fa241d70c6e1bf45a4fec893ad62f3f1595365","tid":308653,"uid":53559,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T12:11:04.000Z","msg":"Book 左酒店去到先話冇房得幾個情況:<br />\n1) 岩岩先起booking, agent 未send 得切reservation order (RO) (好多人以為上網經agent book 會即刻有房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  其實要即刻有房最快會係經酒店到直接book)<br />\n2) Agent on99 冇send RO/RO 錯名/黎check in 既人同訂房深個名唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3) 去錯酒店 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n4) 訂錯日期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n諗到再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: 5星酒店FO"},{"pid":"80bf00dfd270b2f99529f4e779ccba2f9a556306","tid":308653,"uid":8435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T12:15:58.000Z","msg":"早一晚官網訂，第二日下晝去checkin話無reocrd<br />\n俾我哋入vip room坐住等<br />\n等咗半個鐘都未搵到，話個system未咁快update到<br />\n就咁俾匙我上房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1638cb728442b3b9a9bf7d498cf93740ef1a39e3","tid":308653,"uid":10398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T12:38:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>次次book完都會send email問<br />\n就算唔係所會print定張單到時可以show比reception睇</blockquote><br />\n比張單佢睇 佢都可以唔認你張單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你要咁講冇野好講架喎, 如果佢真係咁都唔認冇辦法架喎<br />\n你唔通BOOK兩間咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79bc18830d2848e23f5084cbe4372c7965c8d1e8","tid":308653,"uid":23235,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T12:44:44.000Z","msg":"試過卜二千米山頂酒店 <br />\n去到話冇record<br />\n山頂入夜得幾度<br />\n差d要訓野外"},{"pid":"b10afbd1500357379b7b0c3e6e82de76542a5b9e","tid":308653,"uid":70946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T13:00:37.000Z","msg":"試過一次去大陸旅行，上網book左，去到話唔招待外賓，但網度又冇提示<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c96f429aaaa7a52a37922f772f71bfd2f1fecaaa","tid":308653,"uid":1567,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T13:22:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過一次去大陸旅行，上網book左，去到話唔招待外賓，但網度又冇提示<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n返國內住酒店，事前問清楚係咪招待外賓是常識吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce9cfe1df1ca329df431c89350e0b9bd569bc74b","tid":308653,"uid":22446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T13:26:54.000Z","msg":"好緊張 下星期出發 print左啲單出黎 仲可以做啲咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ab23d61f327bdee70aa6b2ac56f86f9f5a04d03","tid":308653,"uid":22446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T13:27:09.000Z","msg":"Agoda伏唔伏？"},{"pid":"1bf330ce35705131e8a62cc519edc833e426b788","tid":308653,"uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T13:28:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好緊張 下星期出發 print左啲單出黎 仲可以做啲咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n搵定多幾間酒店以防萬一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87dea0c6948dc8cbe8893208d095a493fd53e414","tid":308653,"uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2